---
title: Beef & Mushroom Lasagne with Mozzarella & Leek Béchamel
description: When the weather cools down, the layers come on and mozzarella cheese makes the best cheesy layer to a beef, pork and mushroom filled lasagne. Bundle up your lasagne with flavour and cheese until your tastebuds are warm and cosy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/645d83e7bc8e8873a10d3fbc-804b1716.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/645d83e7bc8e8873a10d3fbc.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/beef-and-mushroom-lasagne-645d83e7bc8e8873a10d3fbc
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 50 minutes
nutrition:
